data.description: Price Reduced to sell!  Don’t wait!  Move in before the end of the year!  The home is ready for its new buyer.  Hard to find quiet corner unit. High ceilings and corner location gives this home an abundance of natural light. Large screened patio/balcony over looks a lush private courtyard below. Rooms are split by a hallway and a full size bathroom for the utmost privacy. Save money with having a Newer AC & Water heater.  Community has many amenities to keep you healthy and busy including several pools, playground, walking paths, theatre, library, BBQ area and tennis courts. HOA also includes HBO cable and water!  Seller would like to close by end of the year.
